## config.txt REQUIRED in Bot directory.

# Contents:

Line1: Botname
Line2: Bot Confirmation secret (for communicating with other bots)
Line3 and onwards: List of channels to join, one per line.

# Example:

MyBot
ILOVEBEES
#spawn
#mychannel
#channelwithpw thepassword

## lp.txt OPTIONAL with content for !lp list

# Contents:

Each Line:
NAME URL

# Example:

Superawesome http://www.youtube.com/superawesomegamer
LPEliteExpert http://www.youtube.com/user/lpeexpert

## twitterkeys.txt OPTIONAL, but REQUIRED if you want to parse twitter links

# Contents:

Line1: Access Token
Line2: Access Token Secret
Line3: Consumer Key
Line4: Consumer Key Secret